// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1748 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 369a7648-832b-553d-9177-c1b802dfa5bb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
